# Level 2 Workflow: Feature Enhancement

This document outlines the process for implementing Level 2 complexity tasks in the AgenticFleet project. Level 2 tasks involve feature enhancements, small new features, or moderate improvements to existing functionality.

## Level 2 Task Characteristics

- Adding new features to existing components
- Enhancing existing functionality
- Moderate code changes affecting multiple files
- UI/UX improvements
- Test coverage expansion
- Performance optimizations

